      • parseName

        public void parseName(String cpeName)
               throws UnsupportedEncodingException

        Parses a name attribute value, from the cpe.xml, into its corresponding parts: vendor, product, version, update.

        Example:

           cpe:/a:apache:struts:1.1:rc2

        Results in:

        • Vendor: apache
        • Product: struts
        • Version: 1.1
        • Revision: rc2
        Overrides:
        parseName in class IndexEntry
        Parameters:
        cpeName - the cpe name
        Throws:
        UnsupportedEncodingException - should never be thrown...
